狗狗個名 再命令佢地執行主人既指示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cb0fb5b15444b195c2ddfd971dd7dbff697ee7","tid":1220993,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"1.漂白水<br />\n班警察哥哥日日被班暴徒亂dum雜物 件衫都污糟晒 我地班好市民要自發帶漂白水俾佢地可以即場漂番靚件衫衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.醋<br />\n呢幾日都見到班警察哥哥叫白切雞飯盒食 啲飯淡而無味 食玩邊有心機同氣力去嚴懲班暴徒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好加小小醋調下味，食完之後容光煥發，勇武向前， 班暴徒見到自然不攻自退。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啊唔記得提番句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一路蘸醋一路漂白好似會好大件事<br />\n千奇唔好亂試</span></span>"},{"pid":"bae7c9812b22b7c70951e9a815129a6f1463b01e","tid":1220993,"uid":202317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cb0fb5b15444b195c2ddfd971dd7dbff697ee7","tid":1220993,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"1.漂白水<br />\n班警察哥哥日日被班暴徒亂dum雜物 件衫都污糟晒 我地班好市民要自發帶漂白水俾佢地可以即場漂番靚件衫衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.醋<br />\n呢幾日都見到班警察哥哥叫白切雞飯盒食 啲飯淡而無味 食玩邊有心機同氣力去嚴懲班暴徒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好加小小醋調下味，食完之後容光煥發，勇武向前， 班暴徒見到自然不攻自退。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啊唔記得提番句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一路蘸醋一路漂白好似會好大件事<br />\n千奇唔好亂試</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"係咁撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb469f6a4d170f3a9771a4220320fc574fbad9c0","tid":1220993,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cb0fb5b15444b195c2ddfd971dd7dbff697ee7","tid":1220993,"uid":198389,"like":